# whisper.cpp Vulkan Windows binaries are dropped here by the release CI
# step (see .github/workflows/release.yml).  Local dev: see setup.bat.
#
# Expected files when the GPU backend is enabled:
#   whisper-server.exe
#   ggml.dll
#   ggml-base.dll
#   ggml-cpu.dll
#   ggml-vulkan.dll
#   whisper.dll
#   (plus any other DLLs whisper.cpp's Vulkan build emits)
